original: Zielfelt, Einar, statens lantbruksingenjör, Växjö, f. 14/8/98 i Kullerstad, Östergötl. 1., av kapt. Hj. Z. o. Fred-rique v. Boisman. G. 1. 29 m. Ingrid Nordberg; 2. 35 m. Ingegerd Wilner, Barn: Ann-Charlotte f. 31, Monica 32, Lars 37, Karin 42. — Stud:ex. i Norrköp. 18, stud. v. KTH 18-21, v. Alnarps lantbr:inst. 21-22. E. lantbr:ing. i Västerb. 1. 28, tf. lantbr:ing. i Östergötl. 1. 31-33, i Kronob. 1. 33, statens lantbr:ing. i Växjö fr. 33.
translated:
Zielfelt, Einar, state agricultural engineer, Växjö, born on August 14, 1898 in Kullerstad, Östergötland. Son of Captain Hj. Z. and Fredrique v. Boisman. Married 1. in 1929 to Ingrid Nordberg; 2. in 1935 to Ingegerd Wilner. Children: Ann-Charlotte, born in 1931; Monica, born in 1932; Lars, born in 1937; Karin, born in 1942. 

Education: Graduated from high school in Norrköping in 1918, studied at the Royal Institute of Technology from 1918 to 1921, and at the Alnarp Agricultural Institute from 1921 to 1922. 

Work experience: Agricultural engineer in Västerbotten from 1928, acting agricultural engineer in Östergötland from 1931 to 1933, agricultural engineer in Kronoberg in 1933, state agricultural engineer in Växjö since 1933.
